EL1-5e: I did, as well. Last night, I think I dreamed.
<<setVex vexSurprised>>
VEX: Oh? What of?
<<setRobo roboNeutral>>
EL1-5e: Hard to define in words you would understand. I saw shapes and blurs, and felt something. . . warm. Pliable. Comfortable.
<<setVex vexThinking>>
VEX: Comfortable, hmm?

