title: Maintenance6
---
VEX: Well, you’re currently composed of a set of mismatched parts. Each time I leave you alone for a significant period of time, I’ve got to make sure that everything is still working properly before I really get in the weeds with you.
VEX: Sort of like tuning an old guitar.
<<endDialogue end>>
