EL1-5e: VEX. May I ask a question?
EL1-5e: How close are you with ELISE?
VEX: Ah. That’s. . . 
EL1-5e: Ow.
VEX: Apologies.
VEX: We used to be much closer when we were younger.
<<endDialogue end>>
