EL1-5e: Is she not happy that you are trying to help her?
VEX: No she. . . she has a different mindset.
EL1-5e: Ouch!
VEX: Sorry. I’m getting distracted.
VEX: She, um. . . she doesn’t understand the beauty in a continued legacy.
VEX: Instead she worships the temporary nature of the frail human body.
VEX: Which is something I hate.
<<endDialogue end>>
