VEX: How good it is that she has me.
VEX: Myself, who is willing to throw away everything to save her life.
VEX: I can’t stand it.
VEX: . . . Sorry, you’re in pain, aren’t you, EL1? 
VEX: Talking about these things tends to tighten my grip unintentionally. My apologies. Hahaha.
VEX: Calibration complete.
<<endDialogue end>>
